This paper presents a model and methodology for learning paraphrastic sentence embeddings directly from bitext, which is a common task in natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on NLP and related topics. The paper also discusses the performance of the model in cross-lingual tasks, which suggests that it may be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
